# Development Tools and Configuration

## ESLint Configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint rules and settings
- Automatic removal of unused imports
- TypeScript-specific rules
- Angular-specific rules

## Prettier Configuration
- [.prettierrc](mdc:.prettierrc) - Code formatting rules
- Single quotes for strings
- 2 spaces for indentation
- 100 character line width
- Trailing commas in objects and arrays

## Package Management
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- Use npm for package management
- Keep dependencies up to date
- Follow semantic versioning

## Build and Development
- Use Angular CLI for development
- Follow Angular's build optimization guidelines
- Implement proper error handling
- Use environment-specific configurations

